window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Matteo Bianchi</b></p> <p>I chose to believe in fate.</p> <p>Akira Wright was the love of my life, but I wasn't so sure we were meant to be together in this lifetime. She'd been in her most vulnerable state when our paths first crossed.</p> <p>A bond I thought was strong enough to convince her she'd always been meant for me was forged, but in the end, I had to walk away, and she let me.</p> <p><b>Akira Wright</b></p> <p>I chose to ignore fate.</p> <p>Matteo Bianchi might be the love of my life, but how was I supposed to love him when I promised forever to my husband? He'd come into my life at a time when loving another wasn't a part of my endgame.</p> <p>The bond we'd forged changed me forever, but it hadn't been enough to bring me out of my despair. In the end, he walked away, and I let him.</p> <p><i>Sinful Surrender </i>is book three in the Mafia Misfits series and can be enjoyed as a standalone.</p> <p>Contains mature content.</p>"; 
